metadata.dc:description: The prosthetic loads in removable partial dentures are analyzed. Different clinics and laboratory methods to make retain and support are discussed. From its study is infered a therapeutic prognostic.
metadata.dc:title: Cargas protésicas a considerar en el diseño biomecánico de la prótesis parcial removible.
[Prosthetic loading considered in the biomechanical design of removable partial dentures].
